OL,3,CElectric car owners unhappy with
OL,4,Ccharging infrastructure ` survey
OL,6,FOne Which? member said they could not
OL,7,Fuse a charger because it required an
OL,8,Fapp to be downloaded and their phone
OL,9,Fhad poor signal.
OL,11,FAnother described public charging
OL,12,Finfrastructure as "dismal", claiming
OL,13,Fit is "infinitely more complex" to
OL,14,Fcharge an electric car than buy petrol.
OL,16,FIn July last year the Government
OL,17,Fintroduced legislation enabling
OL,18,Felectric car drivers to only need one
OL,19,Fapp to pay for public chargepoints
OL,20,Foperated by different companies, and
OL,21,Fto use contactless payments.
