OL,6,F"The Government and chargepoint
OL,7,Foperators must continue working
OL,8,Ftogether to ensure the UK's charging
OL,9,Finfrastructure is up to scratch.
OL,11,F"Charging must be easy and reliable to
OL,12,Fsupport more people to make the move
OL,13,Fto an electric car."
OL,15,FWhich? surveyed 1,004 of its members
OL,16,Fin November last year who own a pure
OL,17,Felectric or plug-in hybrid vehicle.
