OL,6,FDepartment for Transport (DfT) figures
OL,7,Fpublished on Wednesday show there were
OL,8,F53,677 public electric vehicle
OL,9,Fcharging devices in the UK at the
OL,10,Fstart of this year, an increase of 45%
OL,11,Ffrom 12 months earlier.
OL,13,FA DfT spokeswoman said the UK is on
OL,14,Ftrack to "install 300,000 public
OL,15,Fchargepoints by 2030".
