OL,6,FShe added: "Our new public chargepoint
OL,7,Fregulations will ensure simpler
OL,8,Fpricing information and payment
OL,9,Fmethods, and will require all rapid
OL,10,Fchargepoints to be 99% reliable on
OL,11,Faverage.
OL,13,F"While we expect the private sector to
OL,14,Fdeliver the majority of chargepoints,
OL,15,Fwe continue to work closely with them
OL,16,Fto expand and improve the network `
OL,17,Fwith our Zero Emission Vehicle mandate
OL,18,Fgiving the private sector the
OL,19,Fcertainty they need to invest in more
OL,20,Fchargepoints."
